  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Field Application Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Attend to customer issues on quality or technical related matters.</li><li>Conduct seminars on product or technical usage.</li><li>Coordinate with customers and Business Division to enable Panasonic products to be spec-in for customer requirements.</li><li>Trouble-shoot technical issues and provide solutions to customers.</li><li>Updates to Business Division on customer current and future requirements for product development.</li><li>Communication with Business Divisions to understand new product launch for customer introduction.</li><li>Leadership and team management to ensure successful project implementation.</li><li>Align technical decisions with business goals</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>Strong technical knowledge in Energy related domain.</li><li>Well versed product characteristics and performance.</li><li>Work closely with sales for project execution.</li><li>Experience in project management.</li><li>Stay updated on technology transformation and learn new developments.</li><li>3 to 5 years’ experience in related industry.</li><li>Degree or Diploma in computer or technology related field or equivalent.</li><li>Proficient in spoken and written Japanese.</li><li>Able to work under stress.</li></ul><p></p>",
